{"service_name": "IT and Information Control Frameworks", "service_id": "7046089560040996", "company_name": "Leicestershire Health Informatics Service", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Leicestershire Health Informatics Service\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     IT and Information Control Frameworks\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    The LHIS IT and Information control frameworks service provides organisations with control frameworks to promote good practices and ensure regulatory compliance. LHIS can both support organisations to utilise toolsets to implement control frameworks and to define tailored control sets to meet organisational goals and objectives.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Development of control frameworks to meet agreed objectives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Packaging of controls into policies to support organisational security\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Audit and assurance around existing control frameworks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Control mapping to organisational frameworks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Preventative, Detective and Corrective controls\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review of existing controls to provide a gap analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Action plan development from gap analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support implementing action plans\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Packaging of controls in policies and procedures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Benchmarking advice and provision of best practice guidance\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Protects the confidentiality, integrity and/or availability of information\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Valuable tool ensuring security planning, implementation, testing, monitoring\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supports business continuity planning and processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Demonstrate compliance with frameworks e.g. COBIT, ISO27001, PCI DSS, ITIL\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Standardisation of security practices and processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supports organisational security strategies and roadmaps\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Recommendations on best practice\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3600 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93307/7046089560040996-pricing-document-2015-09-14-1144.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93307/7046089560040996-sfia-rate-card-2015-09-14-1144.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93307